

Aberlour A'bunadh

Nose: Holy cherry and alcohol batman! 
Taste: Thick in the mouth. High ABV (60%)
Finish: Dry, waxy Black Forest Twin Cherries candy. Hot damn! The waxiness is a tad offputting.

toasty sweetness

A (90-100): I taste colors
B (80-89): Hit your marks, find your light and don't be a diva
C (70-79): Some good stuff, some bad stuff
D (60-69): More bad than good
F (0-59): The horror, the horror
